#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to the Invoice App, you can manage your invoices. You have "
"many possibilities to streamline your invoicing process:"
msgstr ""
"In de Facturatie-app kun je je facturen beheren. Er zijn veel mogelijkheden "
"om je facturatieproces te stroomlijnen:"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>CRM App</strong></font>, you "
"create a new opportunity for Emily, recording her contact details and the "
"reason for consultation (e.g. anxiety, stress management, burnout)."
msgstr ""
"In de <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><strong>CRM-app</strong></font> maak je "
"een nieuwe verkoopkans aan voor Emily waarin je haar contactgegevens een de "
"reden van de consultatie registreert (bv. angst, stressmanagement, burn-out)."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model:crm.stage,name:mental_therapy.crm_stage_5
msgid "Inactive"
msgstr "Inactief"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice yourself, manually."
msgstr "Factureer handmatig."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"It helps you manage patients/clients, appointments, schedules, and invoicing "
"in one integrated system, designed for mental therapy practices with "
"flexible sessions, relationship-focused care, and secure patients/clients "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Met dit pakket beheer je cliënten, afspraken, planning en facturatie in één "
"geïntegreerd systeem, ontworpen voor mentale gezondheidstherapie met "
"flexibele sessies, klantgerichte zorg en veilige opslag van gegevens van "
"cliënten."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Let's Try"
msgstr "Testen"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model:mail.template,subject:mental_therapy.booking_suggestion
msgid "Looking forward to meeting you"
msgstr "Ik kijk ernaar uit je te ontmoeten"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Marketing Automation </font></strong>,"
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email Marketing</font></strong>,"
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Social Media Marketing </font></"
"strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing </font></"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Beheer al je communicatiekanalen op één plek met Odoo <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketingautomatisering</font></strong>, "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-mailmarketing</font></strong>, "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media-marketing</font></"
"strong> en <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Sms-marketing</font></"
"strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font></"
"strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Beheer je boekhouding eenvoudiger dan ooit met een volledig geïntegreerde "
"omgeving. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Boekhouding-app</font></"
"strong>)"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your team's and integrate them in all processes by adding "
"the<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Employees App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Beheer je team en integreer ze in alle processen via de<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Werknemers-app</font></strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Move or reschedule the appointment (the patient is notified automatically)"
msgstr ""
"De afspraak verplaatsen of opnieuw inplannen (de cliënt wordt automatisch op "
"de hoogte gebracht)"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to manage your entire "
"business from your phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo is volledig geïntegreerd in een app. Download de app om je hele bedrijf "
"vanaf je telefoon te kunnen beheren."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo biedt je oneindig veel mogelijkheden, zoals:"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Dit is natuurlijk slechts een overzicht van de functies in dit pakket. Je "
"kunt gerust nieuwe apps toevoegen, demodata verwijderen/wijzigen en alles "
"uitproberen!"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once an appointment is booked, you can see it in the <strong>Calendar App</"
"strong>."
msgstr "Geboekte afspraken kun je bekijken in de <strong>Agenda-app</strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your patients/clients easily with the "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App </font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Organiseer evenementen en kom gemakkelijk in contact met je cliënten met de "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Evenementen-App</font></strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model:product.template,name:mental_therapy.product_product_3_product_template
